As Featured in the Halloween 2016 Tiltbrush Showcase!

I found the files for this in old emails, so I thought I'd upload it. This was done way before Poly was a thing, and was likely only finished because a Google rep approached me and asked to feature it.

Looking back at it now, I have absolutely no clue how I did this.~

(The original piece was called 'Pumpkaboo Place', because it was 100% a Pokmon reference.
